  "content": "<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Glenwood to Silver City</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel1\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic01.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                          class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>The morning with weather threatening</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic02.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Glad I'm on the road</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic03.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Gila Wilderness</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic04.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>The cows were not concerned</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic05.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Mogollon Mountains to the east\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRolling along west of the divide. Even the climb I had in front of me couldn't bother me. The final climb of\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthe day\n\t\t\t\t\t\tand the ride was 1,500 feet over 15 miles.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic06.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Looking west\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tNo much left to say. It was a nice day, I thought I could be done by noon or so and I was on a hard track.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic07.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Yucca flaccida\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic08.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Easier to smile when you only have about 120 miles to go.\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic09.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Birds circling\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic10.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Really big crows/ravens waiting on a meal.\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>I saw these birds circling from pretty far off. They would land but then get spooked when a car came\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tby. When I final got up to there postion there was a bobcat which had been there for a while. I\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tconsidered cutting off his tail but 59 yer old Jim realized it wasn't something I really needed.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The last divide crossing just outside of Silver City. It really was almost all down hill from here.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic11.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">This was the last time I climbed up over 6,000 feet\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Taking the easy way</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I arrived in Silver City about noon and went right to <a href=\"www.gilahikeandbike.com\">Gila Hike &\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBike</a>. Driving a Dodge truck into the Gila Wilderness sounded like a nice way to spend my afternoon.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEnterprise was going to pick me up at the hotel but didn't arrive until 3pm. So even though the signs said\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthe park was a two hour drive and it closed at 4 pm I went anyway and was not disappointed.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel2\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic12.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Great view after cresting into the Gila River watershed</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic13.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Gila River watershed</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic14.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Gila River watershed</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic16.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon rain was the rule at this point</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                            <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                            </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Driving up to the Gila Cliff Dwellings National Monument was a great treat. It was the first time in a\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmonth I was driving a vehicle and listening to music without air whistling (among other things) in my\n\t\t\t\t\t\tears.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel3\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic17.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Above the Gila River</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic18.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Gerranimo's birthplace was in this valley</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic19.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>A narrow corridor along the river</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic20.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>The river becomes a meadow</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                            <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                            </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"section-heading\">Gila Cliff Dwellings National Monument</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic21.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I stopped at the Visitor Center and even though they were just closing up the Ranger was very helpful in\n\t\t\t\t\t\tpointing me on my way. I didn't have time to visit the big cliff dwelling but there was one that was a short\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdrive and a short hike away.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic22.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">The door opening was about 3 feet.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/mapcliffdwellings.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">NP service map</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tHard to imagine that this was someone's home.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic24.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Hiking back to the car across from the cliff dwelling</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic25.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAfter 35 days still enjoyed looking at the mountains ...\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic26.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t... and the various other formations that happened to pop into view.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic28.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day35/day35pic29.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Looking south over Silver City\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Text by <a href=\"http://www.havingadventures.com/\">Jim O'Brien</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t. Photographs by Jim O'Brien<a href=\"https://flic.kr/s/aHsk9CwBC1\">TD on Flickr</a>.</p>"
}